  "detailed_description": "<i>SkyScrappers is a classic arcade-style, vertically scrolling, competitive fighting game. Select from a diverse range of extreme sportspeople, to fight and race your way to the top of a falling skyscraper… as it is being demolished.</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/403460/extras/0151b2449679202a7c5c7ef1700e2748.poster.avif?t=1576666421\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/403460/extras/0151b2449679202a7c5c7ef1700e2748.webm?t=1576666421\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/403460/extras/0151b2449679202a7c5c7ef1700e2748.mp4?t=1576666421\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Play with up to four players in classic couch-multiplayer, <strong>now available with steam remote play to coach co-op online with friends.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/403460/extras/e373f086a1c866a614f696ae70480065.poster.avif?t=1576666421\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/403460/extras/e373f086a1c866a614f696ae70480065.webm?t=1576666421\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/403460/extras/e373f086a1c866a614f696ae70480065.mp4?t=1576666421\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>With four campaigns, learn the stories of our fighters and how their paths cross! <strong>Alternately just set up a skirmish with AI bots</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/403460/extras/a592d9b858a7c1f2255da53736bf6638.poster.avif?t=1576666421\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/403460/extras/a592d9b858a7c1f2255da53736bf6638.webm?t=1576666421\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/403460/extras/a592d9b858a7c1f2255da53736bf6638.mp4?t=1576666421\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Classic arcade feel and style<br></li><li>Breathtaking hand-drawn artwork<br></li><li>60fps action<br></li><li>Skill-based gameplay<br></li><li>Full controller support<br></li><li>1-4 Player Local Multiplayer<br></li><li>Single player story mode</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<i>SkyScrappers is a classic arcade-style, vertically scrolling, competitive fighting game. Select from a diverse range of extreme sportspeople, to fight and race your way to the top of a falling skyscraper… as it is being demolished.</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/403460/extras/0151b2449679202a7c5c7ef1700e2748.poster.avif?t=1576666421\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/403460/extras/0151b2449679202a7c5c7ef1700e2748.webm?t=1576666421\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/403460/extras/0151b2449679202a7c5c7ef1700e2748.mp4?t=1576666421\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Play with up to four players in classic couch-multiplayer, <strong>now available with steam remote play to coach co-op online with friends.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/403460/extras/e373f086a1c866a614f696ae70480065.poster.avif?t=1576666421\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/403460/extras/e373f086a1c866a614f696ae70480065.webm?t=1576666421\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/403460/extras/e373f086a1c866a614f696ae70480065.mp4?t=1576666421\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>With four campaigns, learn the stories of our fighters and how their paths cross! <strong>Alternately just set up a skirmish with AI bots</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/403460/extras/a592d9b858a7c1f2255da53736bf6638.poster.avif?t=1576666421\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/403460/extras/a592d9b858a7c1f2255da53736bf6638.webm?t=1576666421\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/403460/extras/a592d9b858a7c1f2255da53736bf6638.mp4?t=1576666421\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Classic arcade feel and style<br></li><li>Breathtaking hand-drawn artwork<br></li><li>60fps action<br></li><li>Skill-based gameplay<br></li><li>Full controller support<br></li><li>1-4 Player Local Multiplayer<br></li><li>Single player story mode</li></ul>",
